{"tid":2060368,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局：我是本港教育政策制訂者、發展者、執行者、檢討者及監察者","createTime":"2020-06-11T14:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T13:28:38.000Z","uid":7542,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7a609735feebba098f7a0ac12df9b74be32255cc","tid":2060368,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T14:51:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁教育局出埋卷，OK？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n新學年起，教育局要求新入職及現職中小學教師接受培訓。其中新入職教師要在3年內完成30小時由教育局提供的核心培訓課程，涉及價值觀、操守、國家及國際教育發展等。教協質疑，教育局有政治目的，擔心課程是政治灌輸。<br />\n<br />\n教育局晚上在網站發表文章，不點名批評有自稱教育專業的組織凡事政治化，把推動教師專業發展的措施「妖魔化」，表示極度遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n對於教協質疑教育局只是行政執行機構，不是學術專業機構，教育局回應，局方是<strong>本港教育政策制訂者、發展者、執行者、檢討者及監察者</strong>，推動教師持續專業發展是職責所在，就本港教育政策和措施等課題提供培訓，是理所當然、責無旁貸。有關的質疑是故意貶低教育局的角色，達到政治抹黑目的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n---------<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q74yKaeTqB0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQ74yKaeTqB0&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0oGpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=3ce15369\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q74yKaeTqB0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531550-20200611.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531550-20200611.htm&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0oGpPR2DWAUw81xbwDiv9SI%3D&h=af3a9937\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531550-20200611.htm&h=0e0b97d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531550-20200611.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1a4828f12a5ff7ad1d67331392d47927112ce517","tid":2060368,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:08:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a81e85ef157c